Special Collections / Rainone copy: Item forms part of the Joseph Rainone Early Comic Collection, a boxed collection arranged by type (almanacs, other serials, monographs) and by size. Almanacs and other serials arranged by title and monographs arranged by year. Purchased on the Bryant Fund.
Publisher's agent's title for Nov., Dec. 1866 issues bound together: Feast of Fun.
